OL,3,CLearner drivers warned about fake
OL,4,Coffers of tests and driving lessons
OL,6,FThe number of learner drivers who have
OL,7,Ffallen victim to offers of fake
OL,8,Fdriving lessons and tests has more
OL,9,Fthan doubled since last year,
OL,10,Faccording to new analysis.
OL,12,FTSB recorded a 211% jump in it's
OL,13,Fcustomers losing money to scams
OL,14,Fincluding fake tests and driving
OL,15,Flesson offers between January and
OL,16,FAugust 2025, compared with the same
OL,17,Fmonths in 2024.
