OL,3,CLearner drivers warned about fake
OL,4,Coffers of tests and driving lessons
OL,6,FThe bank said the average loss for
OL,7,Flearner drivers is #244, but reported
OL,8,Fthat one scam saw an individual pay
OL,9,F#500 up-front for 20 lessons which
OL,10,Fthey did not receive.
OL,12,FTSB also found fraudulent websites
OL,13,Fposing as the Driver and Vehicle
OL,14,FStandards Agency (DVSA), where several
OL,15,Fcustomers paid for a test only to be
OL,16,Fblocked once the payment was made.
OL,18,FA DVSA spokesperson said TSB's data
OL,19,Fshows that there is "a serious and
OL,20,Fgrowing problem" with this type of
OL,21,Ffraud.
