OL,6,FHe advised individuals to watch out
OL,7,Ffor messages claiming to be from
OL,8,Fofficial organisations, or offering
OL,9,F"fast-tracked" tests on social media
OL,10,Fplatforms.
OL,12,FThe current driving test backlogs
OL,13,Fcould be a contributing factor in the
OL,14,Frise of fraudulent driving lesson and
OL,15,Fdriving test services, the bank said.
