OL,3,CLearner drivers warned about fake
OL,4,Coffers of tests and driving lessons
OL,6,FIn July, data from DVSA showed that
OL,7,Flearner drivers are being forced to
OL,8,Fwait more than five months to book a
OL,9,Fslot at four out of five test centres
OL,10,Fin Britain. Some 258 locations, which
OL,11,Fis 81% of all sites, had the maximum
OL,12,Fpossible waiting time of 24 weeks for
OL,13,Fa test as of May 5.
OL,15,FThe ongoing test backlog was initially
OL,16,Fcaused by the pandemic after driving
OL,17,Fschools were forced to stop tests in
OL,18,Fcompliance with Covid-19 lockdown
OL,19,Frules, but the DVSA also attributes
OL,20,Fthe backlog to people booking their
OL,21,Ftest much earlier than before.
